Interface IDefineBinaryImageTag

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICharacterTag, ITag
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefineBitsJPEG2Tag, DefineBitsJPEG3Tag, DefineBitsLossless2Tag, DefineBitsLosslessTag, DefineBitsTag

    public interface IDefineBinaryImageTag
extends ICharacterTag
    Interface for all binary data tags that represent an image. This is used in DefineImage to separate binary image tags from other character tags
